{"tid":300396,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"耶倫：有生之年都不會再發生金融危機","createTime":"2017-06-28T00:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T08:13:44.000Z","uid":98782,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a44433bad08739bfe3560dafbda204789912dda","tid":300396,"uid":98782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:48:06.000Z","msg":"　　《經濟通通訊社２８日專訊》美國聯儲局主席耶倫表示，在她有生之年都不會再發生金融危機，主要因為在２００７年危機後所進行了一連串銀行體系改革。　　耶倫在倫敦一個活動中稱，「或許這話說的太遠，但我真的認為我們現在已安全得多，希望在我們有生之年不會發生危機，至少我覺得不會再發生。」　　美國總統特朗普在競選時承諾會放寬銀行監管，而美國財政部在本月亦建議，放寬大型銀行到的限制。耶倫認為收回自金融危機以來的改革並不是好事，但她未有多作評論。　　另外，耶倫又繼續捍衛聯儲局的循序漸進加息政策，認為雖然經濟面臨不確定性，但較長期而言，儲局的目標仍應是逐步提高利率。（ｍｎ）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN270628231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Dlatest%26newsid%3DETN270628231&d=4CU04Cls7y1y4H5xr4VM4AtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=dd1baab4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN270628231</a><br />\n<br />\n咁咒自己都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775e55f001a919f66967825a8413e4690e5a566e","tid":300396,"uid":49642,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:51:40.000Z","msg":"咁立flag法"},{"pid":"d5f9eb972b042b31929c636e31e9204fd1081d60","tid":300396,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:54:20.000Z","msg":"等睇過幾年金融危機"},{"pid":"9715e78092e9e032efdf5a87000e87c4952ae677","tid":300396,"uid":54433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:55:22.000Z","msg":"香港人終於有方法買平樓"},{"pid":"7131207f1127973446bf2ed2176ea6dccbdde3a5","tid":300396,"uid":30511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:55:59.000Z","msg":"縮短佢有生之年"},{"pid":"1f2e784350f80b8aa050a58b1f9c040623be5bf9","tid":300396,"uid":1